                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-primary-50 p-4 rounded-lg hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <div class="flex items-start mb-2">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-600 mr-2">tips_and_updates</span>
                            <h4 class="font-medium">Keep it concise</h4>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                            Limit your resume to 1-2 pages. Recruiters spend an average of 6
