                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-primary-50 p-4 rounded-lg hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <div class="flex items-start mb-2">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-600 mr-2">tips_and_updates</span>
                            <h4 class="font-medium">Highlight achievements</h4>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                            Use metrics and numbers to quantify your accomplishments and show
                            your impact.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-primary-50 p-4 rounded-lg hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <div class="flex items-start mb-2">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-600 mr-2">tips_and_updates</span>
                            <h4 class="font-medium">Tailor to job description</h4>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                            Customize your resume for each application to match the skills and
                            requirements listed.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-primary-50 p-4 rounded-lg hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <div class="flex items-start mb-2">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-600 mr-2">tips_and_updates</span>
                            <h4 class="font-medium">Use keywords</h4>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                            Include industry-specific keywords to pass through applicant tracking
