                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-primary-50 p-4 rounded-lg hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <div class="flex items-start mb-2">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-600 mr-2">tips_and_updates</span>
                            <h4 class="font-medium">Check formatting</h4>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                            Ensure consistent formatting, proper spacing, and easy-to-read fonts
                            like Arial or Calibri.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-primary-50 p-4 rounded-lg hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <div class="flex items-start mb-2">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-600 mr-2">tips_and_updates</span>
                            <h4 class="font-medium">Proofread carefully</h4>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                            Eliminate spelling and grammar errors. Have someone else review your
                            resume for mistakes.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 text-white">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-6">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0"> <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl">support_agent</span> </div>
                    <div class="flex-grow">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Need help with your resume?</h3>
                        <p class="mb-4">
                            Our career experts can review your resume and provide personalized feedback to help
                            you stand out to employers.
                        </p>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                            <button class="px-4 py-2 bg-white text-primary-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors flex items-center">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined mr-1">chat</span> Chat with Expert
